definition: circle/round/circular/spherical/(of the moon) full/unit of Chinese currency (yuan)/tactful/to make consistent and whole (the narrative of a dream or a lie)

sentences.english: On the left you can easily see the huge shadow of the mountain's conical shape.
sentences.chinese: 你能輕易看出左邊是山峯的巨大圓錐形倒影。

sentences.english: Fruit medium to large elongated conical, tuberculate , light green, flavor good.
sentences.chinese: 果實中等大，長圓錐形，塊狀，淺綠色，風味好。

sentences.english: Belugas have 40 small conical teeth which they use to grasp fish.
sentences.chinese: 白鯨有40個用來抓魚圓錐形小牙齒。
這個是一座印度圓錐形帳篷。

sentences.english: Lake Atitlán rests at the foot of massive conical volcanoes.
sentences.chinese: 阿蒂特蘭湖位於圓錐形火山羣的腳下。
直根長圓錐形，很少紡錘形。

sentences.english: Herbs annual. Roots conic or spinose.
sentences.chinese: 一年生草本根圓錐形或具刺。

sentences.english: All three seemed sharp and conical in figure.
sentences.chinese: 這三座山都呈尖尖的圓錐形。

sentences.english: At E_(6-30), the genital tubercle become cone—form.
sentences.chinese: 生殖結節由丘狀變成圓錐形。

sentences.english: Stylopodium conic, base margin dilated, undulate.
sentences.chinese: 花柱基圓錐形，基部邊緣擴大，波動。

sentences.english: States having thick rough leaves and long-stalked showy flowers with drooping rays and a conelike center.
sentences.chinese: 美國東部多年生植物，長主莖，亮色花冠，圓錐形花。

sentences.english: This is the type of pyramiding that seems to be exhibited by the conical scutes.
sentences.chinese: 這種原因造成的隆背的盾板看起來是圓錐形的。

sentences.english: Mount Muhavura, the first of the volcanoes, is a perfect cone .
sentences.chinese: 火山中的第一座穆哈務拉山呈完美的圓錐形。

sentences.english: A hat top is made into a semi-conical structure by soft materials and connected with the brim.
sentences.chinese: 帽頂用軟材料做成半圓錐形結構並與帽沿相連接。

sentences.english: Stylopodium low-conic or discoid, pale yellow.
sentences.chinese: 花柱基淺圓錐形或者盤狀，淺黃。

sentences.english: First, the cone-shaped rock formations complement the similarly shaped balloons.
sentences.chinese: 首先，圓錐形岩層補償了形狀相似的氣球。
